    <h1>HYPERPOEM: A LOVE INDUSTRY</h1>
    <p>
        Love is a whisper, soft and <a href="file:///C:/Users/Administrator/OneDrive/Documents/SWEET.html" target="_blank">sweet</a>,  
        A tender touch, a heart’s <a href="file:///C:/Users/Administrator/OneDrive/Documents/HEARTBEAT.html" target="_blank">heartbeat.</a> 
        It dances in the morning light,
        A warmth that makes the world feel right.

        It’s in the quiet moments shared,  
        In every glance, in how you cared. 
        A <a href="file:///C:/Users/Administrator/OneDrive/Documents/SPARK.html" target="_blank">spark</a> that lights the darkest skies,
        A truth seen deep in lover’s eyes.  

        Love is a journey, wild and free,  
        A force that binds you and me.  
        No need for words, no need for sound,  
        In love, we’re lost, but also found.

        Through every storm, through every <a href="file:///C:/Users/Administrator/OneDrive/Documents/FIGHT.html" target="_blank">fight,</a>
        Love’s gentle hand will hold us tight.  
        And when the world begins to fall,  
        It’s love that lifts us, after all
        </p>
    <p>
